Host Configuration
	* QEMU emulator version 3.1.0 (Debian 1:2.5+dfsg-5ubuntu10.34),  Copyright (c) 2003-2008 Fabrice Bellard
	* qemu-kvm service enabled.

Preparation
  $ source env.sh
  $ export KW=elapsed
  $ export COND=">100000"

Running with KVM

  $ make qemu KVM=1 | r0 | r1 | rf > p2
    # type 'forktest' for enough times and ^A x exit
  $ tail -n +10 p2 > p3
  $ r3 p3
